text: The Liberator () is a 2013 Venezuelan Spanish drama movie directed by Alberto Arvelo and starring Édgar Ramírez, María Valverde, Juana Acosta, Danny Huston, Erich Wildpret, Iwan Rheon, Imanol Arias. ==Other websites== * * * Category:2013 drama movies Category:Venezuelan movies Category:Spanish drama movies
